history.content:
Hi everyone,

Do you want to have your voice heard by faculty, staff, and the Chairs?

HKN and other EECS student organizations have composed the EECS Undergraduate Survey for you to provide input and feedback to the EECS Department. This is a great opportunity for you to make a real impact in your classes, student life, and campus culture.

In addition, you can choose to be entered into a drawing to win one of fifteen (15) $10 Amazon gift cards once you complete the survey.
Note this is a different from the CRA survey sent out recently. This survey is focused on improving the EECS department and student life.
Your response is completely anonymous. We encourage you to respond honestly and openly!

The survey is available here: https://berkeley.qualtrics.com/SE/?SID=SV_2nHVRhUV8Ws18Pj
